      "raw_text": "take steps to secure a share Of the\nbounty for Washington, Oregon and\nIdaho, these states having been nam\ned as beneficiaries under the law.\n\n\nThe chamber of commerce took the\ninitiative and asks for the co-opera-\nton of every chamber of commerce,\ncommercial club, farmer, business\nman and capitalist in the states\nnamed.\n\n\nMaxwsll's Speech.\n\n\nMr. Maxwell spoke upon The Flu\nture OF the Great Northwest-Irriga-\nton, Education, Forestry and Homes\nof the Land\" The speaker is a men,\nDer of the National Irrigation associa-\ntion and an expert upon the subject.\nHe is one of the best informed men\nin the United States on irrigation, is\na fluent talker and carried weight\nwith his hearers.\n\n\nAt 8 O'Clock this evening there will\nbe banquet and the committee in\ncharge has provided to serve 400\nguests."
